And In "Camera Settings" set "Video Resolution" to "4K 17:9"
And In "Camera Settings" set "Frame Rate" to "12 FPS"
And In "Camera Settings" set "Field of View" to "WIDE"
And In "Capture Settings" switch "Spot Meter" to "ON"
And In "Capture Settings" switch "Upside Down" to "ON"
Then Verify, that the Mode Label displays "4K 17:9 / 12 FPS / W Â°"
Then verify from the CameraRoll count of thumbnails is "1"
Then select from the CameraRoll the last thumbnail
Then verify thumbnail is not playable
Then verify thumbnail "High Res" can download
Then verify from Album the count of thumbnails is plus "1"
Then select from Album the last thumbnail
Then Delete from Album the last thumbnail
